latestPosts.caption:
Here’s a highlight from ASOS – “A Summer of Style” at Lakmē Fashion Week in partnership with FDCI.

ASOS presents A Summer of Style, celebrating bold trends for the season. Artistic Garden takes a maximalist approach to nature with rich earthy tones, botanical influences, and ornate embellishments. Refined Resort embodies high summer elegance with sun-scorched hues, romantic organza, intricate lace, and luxury linens. Glassmorphic brings playful energy with jeweled florals, luxe jacquards, and statement mini dresses in fresh blues and sugary pinks. Finally, Monochrome redefines black tie with the BTD (Black Tie Dress), pairing modern tuxedos with luxurious lace and dazzling sequins for the ultimate RSVP look.
